OL,3,CGatwick Airport's second runway legal
OL,4,Cchallenge to be heard at High Court
OL,6,FA legal challenge over plans for a
OL,7,Fsecond runway at Gatwick Airport is
OL,8,Fset to be heard at the High Court
OL,9,Flater today.
OL,11,FThe Gatwick Area Conservation Campaign
OL,12,Fand campaign group Communities against
OL,13,FGatwick Noise Emissions (Cagne), are
OL,14,Ftaking legal action against the
OL,15,FDepartment for Transport (DfT) over
OL,16,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander's
OL,17,Fdecision in September to approve the
OL,18,Fplans.
