OL,3,CGatwick Airport's second runway legal
OL,4,Cchallenge to be heard at High Court
OL,6,FThe privately funded scheme, costing
OL,7,F#2.2 billion, will see the West Sussex
OL,8,Fairport move its emergency runway 12
OL,9,Fmetres north.
OL,11,FThe move will enable the runway to be
OL,12,Fused for departures of narrow-bodied
OL,13,Fplanes such as Airbus A320s and Boeing
OL,14,F737s, allowing it to be used for
OL,15,Faround 100,000 more flights a year.
