OL,3,CGatwick Airport's second runway legal
OL,4,Cchallenge to be heard at High Court
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the hearing, Sally
OL,7,FPavey, chairwoman of Cagne, said the
OL,8,FTransport Secretary had taken a "rose-
OL,9,Ftinted view" of the planning
OL,10,Fapplication.
OL,12,FShe continued: "It is unrealistic to
OL,13,Fexpect local authorities, and the
OL,14,Ftaxpayer, to continue to meet the
OL,15,Finfrastructure costs of airport
OL,16,Fexpansion and the loss of wellbeing
OL,17,Fdue to ever increasing noise."
