OL,3,CGatwick Airport's second runway legal
OL,4,Cchallenge to be heard at High Court
OL,6,FBarristers for the DfT told a previous
OL,7,Fhearing that some of Mr Barclay and
OL,8,FCagne's arguments were "irrefutably
OL,9,Funarguable".
OL,11,FJames Strachan KC, for GAL, said in
OL,12,Fwritten submissions for the earlier
OL,13,Fhearing: "It is obviously contrary to
OL,14,Fthe public interest that
OL,15,F(unmeritorious) litigation such as
OL,16,Fthese claims should unnecessarily
OL,17,Fdelay national infrastructure projects
OL,18,Fsuch as the proposed development."
